{"comments":"Design Token Infrastructure.\n\nDesign tokens are the atomic units of a design system. They are named values\nwith semantic meaning that can be referenced, composed, and exported to\nvarious formats (CSS custom properties, design tool variables, etc.).\n\n## Token Anatomy\n\nEvery token has:\n- **Name**: Semantic identifier (e.g., \"color.primary.500\")\n- **Description**: Human-readable explanation\n- **Category**: Grouping for organization (e.g., \"color\", \"spacing\")\n- **Value**: The actual design primitive (Color, Dimension, etc.)\n\n## Token Categories\n\nStandard categories follow the pillar structure:\n- `color` — Color values (OKLCH, sRGB, etc.)\n- `spacing` — Spacing values (padding, margin, gap)\n- `size` — Dimension values (width, height)\n- `radius` — Corner radius values\n- `shadow` — Shadow definitions\n- `type` — Typography (font, size, weight, line-height)\n- `duration` — Animation/transition timing\n- `easing` — Easing curves\n- `zindex` — Stacking order\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nTokens enable deterministic composition. When Agent A creates a button\nreferencing `color.primary.500`, Agent B knows exactly what color that is.\nThe token name is the contract; the value is the implementation.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token"],"TokenName"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[120,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Token.purs","start":[120,1]},"title":"eqTokenName"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token"],"TokenName"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[121,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Token.purs","start":[121,1]},"title":"ordTokenName"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token"],"TokenName"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[124,53],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Token.purs","start":[123,1]},"title":"showTokenName"}],"comments":"Semantic token identifier.\n\nToken names follow a hierarchical dot-notation:\n- `color.primary.500`\n- `spacing.md`\n- `type.heading.h1`\n\n## Naming Conventions\n\n- Use lowercase letters, numbers, and dots only\n- No leading or trailing dots\n- No consecutive dots\n- Minimum 2 characters, maximum 128 characters\n\n## Examples\n\n```purescript\nmkTokenName \"color.primary.500\"    -- Just (TokenName \"color.primary.500\")\nmkTokenName \"invalid..name\"        -- Nothing (consecutive dots)\nmkTokenName \"\"                     -- Nothing (too short)\n```\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Token.purs","start":[118,1]},"title":"TokenName"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a token name with validation.\n\nReturns Nothing if the name doesn't follow naming conventions.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token"],"TokenName"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"